><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hLtzF4c.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ivpusf2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zerocoolduff3000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This counts as art, right? My R2-D2.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nmqY2qf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/waku4sE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Took me four years to build it. Full size model.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RdSFXtE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/boLRpr2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V33puIi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lnRD9Rh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oEVRdKW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F93op2s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gLo08Ku.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bk1IMSu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DQnZoDL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AItuGiO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FcXTnlX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IX9FkU7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rLcO1fW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I fabricated a lot of the parts myself with pretty rudimentary tools.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9YUQ3Kk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sA2TOcX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G6pggY8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The feet are all steel. I did not weld these, got them secondhand from another builder.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/303FaDr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/arz7WJ9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HSBsCn8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I had to learn a lot. I knew nothing about servos or RC stuff.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qKqEdN5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ENPOBOh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xHpbIQ3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I designed the legs attachments to come apart so I can transport him in pieces. He weighs about 150 pounds.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LpaWOLH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Abtx1bJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/19Yeivn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Before and after weathering. A clean droid just doesn’t look right to me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OleKT3y.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>When the weather is nice my ten year old son drives him around on the sidewalk and all the neighborhood kids run outside. The plan was to do hospital visits but then the pandemic hit so that’s on hold.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nmqY2qf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LeastViral]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Storm by Jade Cargill</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IwAsf7O</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0wucbg0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4n3agIE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IwAsf7O</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tamerlun]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>vocation: package delivery; avocation: crisis intervention</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SpXHaQU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KzxFnn6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>all in a day’s work</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SpXHaQU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[yakiudon]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Helloooo Salt Lake City, Utah</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wPI958j</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NzSPVfl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(That’s Barbara Corcoran by the way)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wPI958j</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zoraniko]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fun Fact</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MmLZhcG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Xi3hfCi.jpg" style="max-width