c:creator></item><item><title>I neither want nor need the context for this quote</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IGaZkyH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xjoQB4Q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IGaZkyH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NotMyFirstAbortion]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The secret ingredient is crime</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5gEBKBo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8eW4vPV.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5gEBKBo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TurnersClassicMovies]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wood and acrylic portraits… I call my style “Wallffiti”</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qGBmNE2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wTZeJLf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Friend of mine who is a visual artist based in Durham, NC: Candy Carver sent me a photo…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XzNXFSy.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I take the photo into Photoshop and illustrator to add my own style and color space to plan out the painting later…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1avlcKk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The wood is hand sculpted. That’s me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iYixQZW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Table saw, band saw, sander to create my wood template for the design…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4SbVxoA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Design is then printed onto the sculpted wood. Now it’s time to paint…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xxlU3FI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Each individual piece is now hand painted with the aid of an assistant. I work with apprentices via a paid art therapy arrangement.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MLkvdkz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Almost done.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C63VW7k.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Finished.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wsAygMH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Staged at a gallery in Raleigh-The Museum…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wCOrzmD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That’s ALSO a barbershop.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qGBmNE2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[johnsonjoeb]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Saga of the Shakespearian Tea</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZQGH9HK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6hMysXL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uOFauOQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mvmtJiE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b5TOr4l.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/liDdbzC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3tutjPm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SxnU1rh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Stella Tax! She gets blurry in the sno